      <title>亚德尼称标普明年可能触及 6,000 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-25/yardeni-says-s-p-could-hit-6-000-next-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yardeni Research 总裁 Ed Yardeni 表示，明年标普 500 指数可能会达到 6,000 点，而我们现在正处于牛市。他还表示，美联储仍坚持2%的通胀目标。他在“彭博监视”节目中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-25/yardeni-says-s-p-could-hit-6-000-next-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
